	   <tr><td colspan=2>I play an Iksar Monk, awesome class IMO.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is very simple to keep your skills up, I have admittently, gotten lazy with 2hb.<br><br>Every time you lvl throw both weapons in your inv or give to a groupmate to hold.  Max out h2h, its what we do in higher lvls, it sucks in lower lvls.<br><br>Max it out (its only 5 a lvl, goes up fast) then forget the h2h til you lvl again and repeat.<br><br>I am talking about good 1hb/2hb weapons.  I have an essence of dol in off hand.  I usually dont do this method becuase of the essence.  I have no weapon in my off-hand til i get fighting baton :)<br><br>so they both go up at the same time...gota work on my 2hb arg, its only like 5, doh (lvl 15 btw)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
